Package: rjulia
Type: Package
Title: Integrating R and Julia -- Calling Julia from R
Version: 0.9-2
Date: 2015-08-01
Author: Yu Gong [aut, cre], Oliver Keys [ctb], Martin Maechler [ctb]
Maintainer: Yu Gong <armgong@yahoo.com>
Description: An interface between R and Julia.  It allows to run a script
 in julia from R, i.e., call Julia on R objects and provides object type
 mapping between R and Julia.
SystemRequirements: Julia (including C headers [pkgs julia-dev (deb) / julia-devel (rpm)]),
 GNU make
License: GPL-2
Suggests:
  RUnit
